    <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('welcome-page')">Back to Home</button>
    </div>

    <script>
    function showPage(pageId) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.container').forEach(page => page.classList.add('hidden'));
    document.getElementById(pageId).classList.remove('hidden');
    }

    function proceedToInfo() {
    const movie = document.getElementById('movie-select').value;
    const time = document.getElementById('showtime-select').value;
    const name = document.getElementById('user-name').value;

    if (!movie || !time || !name) {
    alert('Please fill all fields!');
    return;
    }

    document.getElementById('movie-title').innerText = movie;
    showPage('movie-info-page');
    }

    function generateSeats() {
    const seatMap = document.getElementById('seat-map');
    seatMap.innerHTML = '';
    const rows = ['A', 'B', 'C', 'D'];
    rows.forEach(row => {
    for (let i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {
    const seat = document.createElement('div');
    seat.className = i <= 5 ? 'seat regular' : 'seat vip';
    seat.innerText = `${row}${i}`;
    seat.addEventListener('click', () => toggleSeatSelection(seat));
    seatMap.appendChild(seat);
    }
    });
    }

    function toggleSeatSelection(seat) {
    seat.classList.toggle('selected');
    updateSeatSummary();
    }

    function updateSeatSummary() {
    const selectedSeats = document.querySelectorAll('.seat.selected');
    const selectedSeatNumbers = Array.from(selectedSeats).map(seat => seat.innerText);
    const totalPrice = Array.from(selectedSeats).reduce((total, seat) => {
    return total + (seat.classList.contains('vip') ? 20 : 10);
    }, 0);

    document.getElementById('selected-seats').innerText = selectedSeatNumbers.join(', ') || 'None';
    document.getElementById('total-price').innerText = totalPrice;
    }

    function sendOTP() {
    alert('OTP sent to your phone number');
    document.getElementById('otp-section').classList.remove('hidden');
    }

    function verifyOTP() {
    alert('OTP Verified!');
    displayTicket();
    }

    function displayTicket() {
    document.getElementById('ticket-movie').innerText = document.getElementById('movie-title').innerText;
    document.getElementById('ticket-date').innerText = new Date().toLocaleDateString();
    document.getElementById('ticket-time').innerText = document.getElementById('showtime-select').value;
    document.getElementById('ticket-seats').innerText = document.getElementById('selected-seats').innerText;
    document.getElementById('ticket-price').innerText = document.getElementById('total-price').innerText;
    showPage('ticket-page');
    }

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    generateSeats();
    });
    </script>
    </body>
    </html>
